headline: Household Products Stocks Q4 Results: Benchmarking Kimberly-Clark (NYSE:KMB)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at household products stocks, starting with Kimberly-Clark (NYSE:KMB).
